SubjectCanada - USA - FATCA ** Agreement **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to bring into force for Canada the AGREEMENT between the Government of Canada and the GOVERNMENT OF THE UNITED STATES OF AMERICA to Improve International Tax Compliance through Enhanced Exchange of Information under the Convention between Canada and the United States of America with Respect to Taxes on Income and on Capital.
